Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lives...? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though that's not \Nsomething you bet on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Yukino-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:13.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's part of Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that Yukino chick have all her marbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though her opponent is Kagura, \Nthe strongest wizard of Mermaid Heel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems she's got confidence to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are sincerely prepared to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then accepting it is the proper thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura versus Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:23.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They bet their lives, so \Nwhoever loses dies, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, things have taken a serious turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}not{\i0} cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I set up a good match if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be a lively battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:48.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your bad luck to be standing \Nbefore a member of Sabertooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is a Celestial Spirit Wizard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Celestial Spirit Wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:02.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden key. One of those \N12 Zodiac Gate things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Fish, I open thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Fish! I like the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Celestial Spirit is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:22.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it was in the Celestial \NSpirit World when we visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going by the usual pattern, it's \Nprobably something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of unsettling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are ones like the Gemini twins too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so my guess is it'll be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling you've hit the mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy will be so pleased!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even a fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, don't waste your time \Ncontradicting that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His stupidity will rub off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}are{\i0} fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:15.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dodging their attacks with \Njust the slightest movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are all kinds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. She's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's no great shakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All she's doing is dodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fro thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not wise to underestimate \NMermaid Heel's strongest wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like it's going to \Nquickly become a fine magic battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! She's deftly dodging \NPisces' fierce attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she escaping the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All she has to do is eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so good at dodging, then \Nall I need to do is ground you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two gates open at the same time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glittering gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:18.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That's one of \Nthe 12 Zodiac Gates, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Scales, I open thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Libra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:36.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Another stunningly \Nbeautiful Celestial Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a sight for sore eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Scales! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:44.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Libra, alter the target's gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gravity manipulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Libra character can \Nuse the same magic as me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So she made Kagura heavier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She blew off Libra's gravity power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her jumping ability is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:26.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Libra...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make the target's gravity go sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:30.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:42.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! She was only able to escape the Celestial \NSpirit's gravity altering for a short time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura is pinned to the statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:55.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm talkin' about! The \Nhighlight of two gates open at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Highlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I wish it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fish stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she out of magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she can use gravity magic too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:33.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura's the one who taught \Nme gravity-altering magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not underestimate Kagura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kagura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, finish 'em all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:50.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the epitome of the Grand Magic Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Kagura is undaunted \Nby two Celestial Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing, isn't it, Yajima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:06.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Experience and grit... She \Ncertainly does have fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited about getting to see a \Nshowdown like this right before my eyes! Cool! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisces, Libra, go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh. This is gettin' monotonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine! The fight is just startin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sting-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yukino's gonna \Nbring out her real power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make me open...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the 13th Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 13th Gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what she just said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Lucy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 12 Zodiac Gates \Nand hence 12 keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard rumors of a 13th key...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and an unknown Celestial Spirit \Nthat's superior to the other 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening the 13th Gate... That \Nmeans you're out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't relied on luck \Nsince the moment I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has come about \Nthrough choices that I've made!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Serpent Bearer, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's leading me to the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ophiuchus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:50.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! I didn't know a \NCelestial Spirit like this existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's humongous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Serpent Bearer?! The thing \Nitself is a serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Ophiuchus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 13th Gate... This is outstanding as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't bode well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:17.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are there two Celestial Spirit \NWizards here, but they both own the 12 Zodiac Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade of Resentment, Archenemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Style of the Unsheathed Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsheathed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really wouldn't want Kagura-chan \Nto unsheathe her sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:50.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a cheap bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, mermaids eat tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-The match is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:39.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is Kagura \NMikazuchi of Mermaid Heel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Kagura-chan could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you not to underestimate Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:52.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Celestial Spirit Wizard is powerful in \Nher own right, but Kagura is just too tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:57.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable, but Sabertooth \Ngot zero points on the second day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Kagura-chan is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the Saber woman weak? Or \Nwas the Mermaid woman strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:11.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The latter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know somebody like her existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:19.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabertooth lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sting-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus ends the second day \Nof the Grand Magic Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raven Tail gained ten points today, \Ngiving them first place with 36 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabertooth gained zero points today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but their 20 points from yesterday \Nkeeps them in second place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, Lamia Scale is tied \Nin second with 20 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mermaid Heel is moving up. They gained ten \Npoints, putting them in fourth place with 19 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fifth place, one rank down, \Nis Blue Pegasus with 17 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in sixth place, one rank \Ndown for them, Quatro Puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Our guild name has \Nbecome Quatro Puppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it. A promise \Nwas made between two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna drink \Nagain tonight! Wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And gaining ten points each, but still \Ntied in last place, are Fairy Tail A Team
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Fairy Tail B Team, both with 12 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of battles are in store for us \Ntomorrow, the third day of the tournament?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were some fine magic battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Celestial Spirit Wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the project is even \Nmore certain to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the second day is over, I haven't \Nsensed the magic power that I perceive every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second day of the \NGrand Magic Games ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five more days until that fateful day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't sense the magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power that was similar to \NZeref's, that we felt every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't sensed it this time, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of many possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it came from a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe they're not in Crocus this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe they're in Crocus, \Nbut not using the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also possible that they're a contestant \Nin the Games, but haven't participated yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that magic is from some kind \Nof device or a set location,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps the device isn't in operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:29.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or there's some sort of filter that \Nkeeps the magic from leaking outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, as long as you don't sense that \Ndangerous power, nothing should happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:41.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll check out the \Norganizers from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:48.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Ultear already reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And try not to get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Goodnight, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:15:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:15.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the day would come \Nwhen we could talk normally like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:27.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten late. Is the \Ndinner party over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' spiffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' spiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:43.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er-chan, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Millianna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Millianna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Mermaid Heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Sho and Wally in the same guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Mermaid \NHeel is a women-only guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:14.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are still traveling. I \Nhear from them once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:20.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It really is great \Nto see you, Millianna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, Er-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er-chan, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is always Wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are good sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gettin' pretty late. We better \Nstart headin' back to the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza hasn't come yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, she is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She mentioned having something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your hands okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' a good night's sleep can't fix!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're wild, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's name is Elfman, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him a message for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him it was a wild battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:25.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An' I'm lookin' forward to goin' up \Nagainst him again during the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him. I wanna fight you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna beat you again next time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Enough already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was having a drinking \Ncontest with Bacchus-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably on the floor over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we woke you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I was thinking about \NSaber's Celestial Spirit Wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:05.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino-san, I think her name is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing. The 12 Zodiac Gates and \Nthe 13th one... I think? Even though she lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they bet their lives, so I was \Nwondering what's gonna happen now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True, it is worrisome...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're in no position \Nto be worried about other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We've still got three days left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. First, we need to \Nfocus on winning and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys got a visitor. They're in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon and... Sherry's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheria-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like it's gonna be a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:08.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Crocus Garden, the inn \Nwhere Sabertooth is staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pitiful that I \Ncan't even cry, you scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember why we're the top wizard guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at the insects around you. \NDon't talk to them. Just crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes are on something far greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:40.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Making the heavens roar. Setting the \Nland aflame. Silencing the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sabertooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Sabertooth's master, Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you just one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever make such \Na pathetic scene again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I swear that I'll \Nmeasure up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:14.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to the member of another guild. \NI brought shame to Sabertooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wagered your life and lost, and not \Nonly that, the enemy took pity on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:43.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:48.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will submit to any punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then throw away everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I will do exactly as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so ended the second day \Nof the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, Fairy Tail emerged as a contender, \Neven while staying in last place,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but on the underside of \Nthe spectacular festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,something most of them never dreamed \Nof was slowly set into motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:59.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pop quiz! Who's going to pay a visit now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:01.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this comin' from?! \NHow the hell would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give you a hint. What are those \Nwhite crystals that fall from the sky in winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:06.31,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,snow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the opposite of yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:08.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put 'em together, you'll \Npretty much have the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:12.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.65,0:24:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Grudges Are Wrapped \Nin the Silence of the Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-no, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you know who it is but \Nyou're saying it weird on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
